            "TableId": "/Game/UI/JournalData/Entries/ST_JournalEntries.ST_JournalEntries",
            "Key": "CadavaberryInfusion",
            "SourceString": "At first glance you might just assume this is poison, for the cadavaberry is a dangerous fruit. Yet, with careful preparation, and an appropriate amount of boiling, the berry can become a sharp, yet not fatal addition to any dessert.\r\n\r\nMixed with water, it becomes an empowering infusion, that puts a sprint in your step. Partially because your body is reminded at just how close it came to death in drinking it, so makes the most of the life it has left.",
            "LocalizedString": "At first glance you might just assume this is poison, for the cadavaberry is a dangerous fruit. Yet, with careful preparation, and an appropriate amount of boiling, the berry can become a sharp, yet not fatal addition to any dessert.\r\n\r\nMixed with water, it becomes an empowering infusion, that puts a sprint in your step. Partially because your body is reminded at just how close it came to death in drinking it, so makes the most of the life it has left."
